                        <header class="text-white">
                            <h3 class="w-max xl:text-4xl border-b-2 border-b-accent border-dashed">Заяц-Беляк</h3>
                            <p class="xl:text-2xl font-semibold whitespace-pre-line">
                                <span>Lepus timidus (Linnaeus, 1758)</span>
                                <span>Отряд Зайцеобразные – Lagomorpha</span>
                                <span> Семейство Зайцевые – Leporidae</span>
                            </p>
                        </header>
                    </div>
                    <button class="bg-white px-10 py-5 rounded-l-[30px] rounded-r-[30px]">
                        <svg width="94" height="38" viewBox="0 0 100 38" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M3.00098 16.5C1.62026 16.5 0.500977 17.6193 0.500977 19C0.500977 20.3807 1.62026 21.5 3.00098 21.5V16.5ZM98.7682 20.7678C99.7445 19.7915 99.7445 18.2085 98.7682 17.2322L82.8583 1.32233C81.882 0.34602 80.2991 0.34602 79.3228 1.32233C78.3465 2.29864 78.3465 3.88155 79.3228 4.85786L93.4649 19L79.3228 33.1421C78.3465 34.1184 78.3465 35.7014 79.3228 36.6777C80.2991 37.654 81.882 37.654 82.8583 36.6777L98.7682 20.7678ZM3.00098 21.5H97.0005V16.5H3.00098V21.5Z" fill="#F1343E" />
                        </svg>
                    </button>
